Qwen3.6 recurrent shrink/expand prompt-cache patch for ROCmFPX fork.

Source: Reddit r/LocalLLM post 1ullrvq / Pastebin E55YG5NS.
Based on upstream PR: ggml-org/llama.cpp#24785.

Same API/body changes as the stock patch, with `tools/server/server-context.cpp`
hunks adapted to the ROCmFPX fork pinned in this repository.

